# Mastermind member count

In the “Join the HTSA Mastermind Community” step, use **490+ members** (not 440+, 470+, or other numbers unless CJ updates this rule).

Example sentence:  
`Request access to the private Facebook Mastermind — where all live coaching call replays are posted and 490+ members support each other 24/7.`
